"Phir gir paray, koi mila na sahara.. kia karain?" Andddd.. "Kia ho gaya.. socha na tha" By Momina. 💖
BET YOU PAKISTAN'S COKE STUDIO IS THOUSAND TIMES BETTER THAN INDIA'S COKE STUDIO ON THE BASIS OF "LYRICS" and "SOUND EDITING". 
PAKISTAN ZINDABAAD. 👏
